signatureAbility.signatureDescription: Defenders with this ability force more catch knockouts and react quicker in any mid-field zone coverage, less than 20 yards from the LoS inside the numbers and 10-20 outside.
Players with this ability are more likely to succeed at and attempt diving catches and swats.
Defenders with this ability allow fewer broken tackles and cause more fumbles when cut-sticking ballcarriers.
Ballcarriers with this ability have steerable juke animations.
Ballcarriers with this ability will frequently attempt to gain extra yards while being tackled
Ballcarriers with this ability have steerable juke and spin animations.
Elite pass rushers are a mix of strength, speed, and tenacity. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their win rate and block shed speed against one-on-one pass blocks.
Defenders with this ability use faster, more dominant pass rush moves while rushing from the edge of the defense.
Defenders with this ability are granted a free pass rush move once per play after spending stamina to perform one
Defenders with this ability use faster run shed moves for a better chance at shedding blocks against outside zone plays.
Players with this ability will recover from the effects of Wear and Tear and fatigue at an increased rate between plays.
Defenders with this ability force more catch knockouts and react quicker in deep zone coverage, 20+ yards from the LoS and inside the numbers.
Defenders with this ability have higher chance to catch uncontested interceptions, and they have unlimited stamina on the return (until using a special move or breaking a tackle).
Defenders with this ability force more catch knockouts and react quicker in deep zone coverage, 20+ yards from the LoS and outside the hash marks.
Receivers with this ability catch more consistently while catching passes 10-20 yards from the LoS, inside the numbers
Receivers with this ability make sharper cuts and frequently win contested catches when covered by linebackers and linemen.
Receivers with this ability catch more consistently while catching passes less than 10 yards from the LoS, inside the numbers
Blockers with this ability will dominantly win impact blocks on screen plays
Blockers with this ability start every new blocking encounter with built-in resistance
Blockers with this ability reduce a rusher's chances of using a quick block shed move while run blocking.
Blockers with this ability are almost guaranteed to win any double team block they are engaged in
